data.description: Nestled on a generous 35-acre expanse, this stunning ranch-style home is a dream come true for horse enthusiasts. Zoned for horses, this property offers a 44x40 barn that can double as a 4 to 6-car garage, currently featuring three 14'x14' horse stalls with runs, a loft room for hay storage, a tack room, and a feed room. The entire property is thoughtfully fenced and cross-fenced, making it ready for your beloved livestock.    Home Features:    Step into an open floor plan that offers endless possibilities. The formal living room features beautiful wood flooring, setting the stage for elegant entertaining.    The kitchen is the heart of the home, boasting an oversized island, custom cabinets, and stunning countertops. Whether you're a culinary enthusiast or a casual cook, this space is a chef's dream come true.    Cozy up by the gas fireplace in the family room, which also features a walkout to a generous wrap-around deck. Enjoy the serenity of your expansive property while entertaining guests or enjoying a quiet evening.    The master suite is a private sanctuary with a separate 5-piece bath, complete with a luxurious garden tub, and a generously sized walk-in closet.    The basement is an entertainer's dream with a spacious second family room/game room that opens to a covered patio. It's the perfect spot for hosting gatherings, game nights, or simply unwinding in style. Fully finished and set up for a successful home business, AirBNB, or "in-law" apartment. The possibilities are endless.     This exquisite rancher home, combined with the vast acreage and horse-friendly amenities, offers an unparalleled opportunity for those seeking a peaceful yet luxurious lifestyle. it's a rare find that won't last long. Contact us today for a private showing and a chance to experience this dream property in person.
